{"title_page": "1977\u201378 Divizia B", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n | country                    = {{ROU}}\n | competition                = [[Liga II|Divizia B]]\n | season                     = 1977\u201378\n | teams                      = 54 (3x18)\n | promoted                   = [[FC Gloria Buz\u0103u|Gloria Buz\u0103u]]<br />[[Chimia R\u00e2mnicu V\u00e2lcea]]<br />[[CS Minaur Baia Mare (football)|Baia Mare]]\n | relegated                  = [[CSM Pa\u0219cani|CFR Pa\u0219cani]]<br />[[FC Dun\u0103rea C\u0103l\u0103ra\u0219i|Celuloza C\u0103l\u0103ra\u0219i]]<br />[[CS Minerul Lupeni|Minerul Lupeni]]<br />[[CSU Dun\u0103rea de Jos Gala\u021bi|CSU Gala\u021bi]]<br />[[Carpa\u021bi Sinaia]]<br />[[Arm\u0103tura Zal\u0103u]]<br />[[CS Boto\u0219ani]]<br />[[CS Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu|Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu]]<br />[[Victoria Carei]]<br />[[Relonul S\u0103vine\u0219ti]]<br />[[Prahova Ploie\u0219ti]]<br />[[CSM Av\u00e2ntul Reghin|Av\u00e2ntul Reghin]]\n | league topscorer           = \n | biggest home win           =\n | biggest away win           =\n | highest scoring            =\n | matches                    = \n | total goals                =\n | longest wins               = \n | longest unbeaten           =\n | longest losses             =\n | highest attendance         = \n | lowest attendance          =\n | average attendance         =\n | prevseason                 = [[1976\u201377 Divizia B|1976\u201377]]\n | nextseason                 = [[1978\u201379 Divizia B|1978\u201379]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1977\u201378 [[Divizia B]]''' was the 38th season of the second tier of the [[Romanian football league system]].\n\nThe format has been maintained to three series, each of them having 18 teams. At the end of the season the winners of the series promoted to [[Liga I|Divizia A]] and the last four places from each series relegated to [[Liga III|Divizia C]].<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesr/roem2hist.html#78 rsssf.com]</ref><ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_b/tables/1977_78.shtml romaniansoccer.ro]</ref>\n\n== Team changes ==\n{{col-begin|width=auto}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===To Divizia B===\n'''Promoted from [[1976\u201377 Divizia C|Divizia C]]'''\n* [[CS Boto\u0219ani]]\n* [[Viitorul Vaslui]]\n* [[Carpa\u021bi Sinaia]]\n* [[FC Delta Dobrogea Tulcea|Tulcea]]\n* [[AFC Rocar Bucure\u0219ti|Autobuzul Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[Muscelul C\u00e2mpulung]]\n* [[CS Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu|Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu]]\n* [[Minerul Moldova Nou\u0103]]\n* [[Victoria Carei]]\n* [[CSM Av\u00e2ntul Reghin|Av\u00e2ntul Reghin]]\n* [[ICIM Bra\u0219ov]]\n* [[CS Gaz Metan Media\u0219|Gaz Metan Media\u0219]]\n\n'''Relegated from [[1976\u201377 Divizia A|Divizia A]]'''\n* [[FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|Rapid Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[AS Progresul Bucure\u0219ti|Progresul Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[FCM Dun\u0103rea Gala\u021bi|FCM Gala\u021bi]]\n{{col-break|gap=5em}}\n\n===From Divizia B===\n'''Relegated to [[1977\u201378 Divizia C|Divizia C]]'''\n* [[CSM Foc\u0219ani|Unirea Foc\u0219ani]]\n* [[CSM Flac\u0103ra Moreni|Flac\u0103ra-Automecanica Moreni]]\n* [[ACS Sticla Arie\u0219ul Turda|Sticla Arie\u0219ul Turda]]\n* [[CSM Borze\u0219ti|Borze\u0219ti]]\n* [[Voin\u021ba Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[Vagonul Arad|Rapid Arad]]\n* [[Minerul Gura Humorului]]\n* [[CSM Olteni\u021ba|SN Olteni\u021ba]]\n* [[CSM C\u00e2mpia Turzii|IS C\u00e2mpia Turzii]]\n* [[CSM R\u00e2mnicu S\u0103rat|Olimpia R\u00e2mnicu S\u0103rat]]\n* [[Tehnometal Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[AS Minerul Cavnic|Minerul Cavnic]]\n\n'''Promoted to [[1977\u201378 Divizia A|Divizia A]]'''\n* [[FC Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti|Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti]]\n* [[FCM T\u00e2rgovi\u0219te|CS T\u00e2rgovi\u0219te]]\n* [[FC Olimpia Satu Mare|Olimpia Satu Mare]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Renamed teams===\n''SC Tulcea'' was renamed as [[FC Delta Dobrogea Tulcea|Delta Tulcea]].\n\n==League tables==\n===Serie I===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_b/tables/1977_78.shtml romaniansoccer.